data.description: Investor Special, no rental restrictions. Appt Only. Step into this charming 4-bed, 2.5-bath brick home nestled in a quiet neighborhood. Boasting spacious bedrooms, a cozy fireplace in the living room and a sunlit sunroom, this residence exudes warmth and elegance. The backyard oasis is an entertainer's dream, featuring a pool for relaxation and a fire pit for cozy evenings under the stars. While the home offers a solid foundation, it needs a bit of TLC and cosmetic enhancements, providing the perfect opportunity for customization. Transform this space into your dream home and embrace the potential it holds. Don't miss the chance to own a piece of tranquility in this inviting neighborhood.
